Teqqar jida: "Ttif ad kkreg, ad skerkkreg."		
Tafettust teqqur. Taqemmuct la tesfituṛ.		
Ččiɣ taktuniya, yefulta yimi-w.		
Ur tett ara akken tibexsisin, ččurent d aḥekka.		
La ḥekkuɣ i gma taluft, yeqqar acḥal i tesɛiḍ.		
Ay afenǧal n lqahwa, a win i d-yettaldayen allen.		
Ḥrec, ger aẓeṭṭa, err lxiḍ i am-d-iqqersen.		
S timmi mačči s yimi.		
Yeqqur uqerruy-is, hder neɣ qqim.		g qqim.
Tettqudur d sser.		
Tuyat, knant. Aṭas i bubbent.		
Aɛebbuḍ d lebḥar, ad as-tiniḍ d tinifift.		
Imi izemmem, allen ldint.		
Ass-agi, d tɣli. D ccɣel seg ṣṣbah almi d tameddit.		
Irgazen, taṣebḥit, kkren ɣar uqleɛ n lḥemmeẓ. Tizwa, nebda-t s urwat.		
Awal-nni, la yeqqaz deg-i irennu.		
Yeffeɣ afus-iw, ur mazal ad berqent fell-as wallen-iw.		
Akken i d-yekcem, mfezwan. Yal wa anda yerra.		
Axxam-nsen, urǧin zegglen tanalt.		
Awal ur t-id-yulu, yebra i wallen-is, yerra d akessar.		
D mm-tceɣlatin, sani tt-terriḍ, teslek iman-is.		
Thegga-d ifeggagen, tirigliwin, iɣunam. Txuṣ-itt kan tyaẓilt.		
Taduḍt, turad, teqqerdec, tellem. Mazal kan ad tt-teẓḍ, ad tuɣal d tacettiḍt.		
Rezfent-d yessetma s warraw-nsent, axxam yeččur, iqerra fuṛen.		
Ccah, la tetteddu tfarres.		
Zik, ay nečča deg tmendekrar deg umkan-agi!		
Ifri n tteryel, yellan nnig temda n userɣi, d arrac kan ara yettawḍen ɣur-s.		
Mačči yiwet n temda i yellan: tamda tazegzawt, tamda n yiɛeṭṭaren, tamda n waman imellalen…		
Mi ara ddukklen iɣallen kullec ad yifsus.		
Ma kkren-as i udrar, ad t-hudden.		
